trans-unit.source: Provides access to add attributes for one specific type to one specific <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 属性を追加する&1; つの特定の種類の&1; つの特定のアクセスを提供<xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref>です。

trans-unit.source: The first time an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> is queried for attributes for a type, if the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> was populated using <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> for that type, the delegate is passed a AttributeCallbackBuilder.
trans-unit.target: 最初に、<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>場合に、型の属性の照会、<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder>を使用してデータを読み込んだ<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>デリゲートには、その型に対する、AttributeCallbackBuilder が渡されます</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A></xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder></xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> removes the callback reference and adds any attribute information provided by calls to <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>コールバック参照を削除し<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>。</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>への呼び出しによって提供されるすべての属性情報を追加します。</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: Adds the contents of the provided attributes to the attribute table that created this builder.
trans-unit.target: 指定した属性の内容をこのビルダーを作成した属性テーブルに追加します。

trans-unit.source: If an attribute conflicts with another attribute already included in the table, the last attribute added replaces previous attributes.
trans-unit.target: 競合する場合は、テーブルに既に含まれている別の属性を持つ、古い属性が最後に追加された属性に置き換えられます。

trans-unit.source: Attributes can be added only to the type specified by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 属性は<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>。</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>で指定された型にのみ追加できます。

trans-unit.source: The attributes that are added to the table.
trans-unit.target: テーブルに追加する属性。
